channel.title: Error loading MoparScape
channel.description:
Ok I downloaded PDK 6.0 and I downloaded MoparScape, turned off my antivirus, restarted my computer, I'm not sure if I deleted my internet cache, but I wen't tools -> delete all, and no matter what I do I get: Sorry, an error has occured whilst loading RuneScape. To fix this try the following (in order): 1. Try closing ALL open web-browser windows, and reloading 2. try clearing your web-browsers cache from tools->internet options 3. try using a different game world 4. try rebooting your computer 5. try selecting a different version Java from the play-game menu. The MoparScape in the webbrowser (non-download) won't work either. The actual Runescape from Runescape.com works fine, but MoparScape doesnt.
WHY WONT MOPARSCAPE WORK?!
>>> I can't even get moparscape to work at all, am I supposed to modify the compile scripts for it?
